text: FC Abdysh-Ata Kant (also called Abdysh-Ata) is a football club from Kant, Kyrgyzstan. The club plays in the Kyrgyzstan League. == History == The club was founded in 1992. Abdysh-Ata has never won a league title, but the club has been second place in the league 5 times, and third place 4 times. Abdysh-Ata is the third most successful club in the Kyrgyzstan Cup, winning the title 4 times: 2007,2009,2011,2015. == Honours == * Champions (3): 2022, 2023, 2024 *Kyrgyzstan Cup (5): 2007, 2009, 2011, 2015, 2022 *Kyrgyzstan Super Cup (1): 2016 == Other websites == *Career stats by KLISF *Profile at sport.kg *Abdysh- Ata page â€“ Sport.kg Category:Kyrgyz football clubs Category:1990s establishments in Kyrgyzstan
